headline_en: Finally, an Indian student named Ramu from Pondicherry University discovered a remedy for COVID-19, which was first approved by the WHO, when he mixed 2 tablespoons of honey and corn juice with 1 tablespoon of peanut powder and proved to be effective for 5 consecutive days.
